extendedInfo.description: At "Fiabee for Business" accounts, the admin user can:â¢ Deny offline caching at the mobile devicesâ¢ Grant read-only permission (can't delete, rename or upload files)â¢ Deny cloud print permissionsâ¢ Deny the installation of the Fiabee Android App.â¢ Remotely wipe the files in the mobile and desktop Fiabee apps.â¢ Create and manage groups for team working.â¢ Generate a random password for one use, among other features.At the Fiabee for individuals:â¢ Print your files from anywhere to any printer using Google Cloud Print.â¢ Backup your contacts.â¢ Take a photo and upload it instantly to your account.â¢ Centralize your photos and files that you have in your social network profiles into one single place (Google Docs, Facebook, Flickr, Picasa). â¢ (When selected) Automatic bulk upload of all your photos to the cloud any time that a wifi connection is detected.â¢ See other Fiabee apps at www.fiabee.com.â¢ Edit from your android device your documents (using any commercial editor for Android) and sync it back to all your devices.â¢ Select which specific files you want to store locally and keep always synced for quick, offline access.â¢ Access, share and manage all your files on the go.â¢ Search across all your devices almost instantly, even when offline.â¢ Drag&Drop files to your Android directly from our HTML5 app (Chrome Web Store).
